org.javautil.dataset
Interface DatasetIterator<T>

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractDatasetIterator, MatrixDatasetIterator, ResultSetIterator, StreamingDatasetIterator
public interface DatasetIterator<T>

All of the get... methods that take an index reference columns relative to 0.
